[
  "Known as the \"King of Diamonds,\" Lev Leviev owns an integrated diamond outfit with mines in places like South Africa & a jewelry boutique in New York.",
  "He made his name undercutting the DeBeers diamond cartel, striking his own deals with diamond-producing countries like Russia and Angola.",
  "Leviev is also the controlling shareholder of Africa Israel Investments, a real estate and construction company listed on the Tel Aviv Stock Exchange.",
  "Leviev was born in Uzbekistan. His Lubavitcher Jewish family fled to Israel in 1971."
]